## Findings
- Successfully reached the registration form and submitted it.
- Observed that `index.html` contains `<script>window.location.href = 'login.html';</script>` on line 11.
- This causes an immediate redirect back to login, making it look like the login/registration failed.
- Plan: Modify `index.html` to only redirect if the user is NOT logged in.
